---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy & Cookie Policy | Horsorion"
  description="Horsorion privacy policy: how we collect, use, store, and protect visitor and client data, and how we use cookies."
  locale="en"
  currentPath="/en/privacy"
>
  <section class="bg-brand-navy py-12 text-white">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Privacy & Cookie Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-shell py-14">
    <div class="prose prose-slate mx-auto max-w-3xl text-sm leading-8">
      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-brand-navy mt-6">Data collected</h3>
      <p>
        When you submit a contact form or request a sample, we collect your name, email address, and any details you provide.
        This is used solely to respond to your enquiry and follow up on commercial discussions.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-brand-navy mt-6">Cookie policy</h3>
      <p>
        This site may use Google Analytics (GA4) for anonymous traffic statistics (page views, referrers, etc.). All data is anonymised and is not used to identify individual visitors.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not use any advertising or cross-site tracking cookies. We do not sell or share data with third parties for advertising. If you do not wish to be measured, please disable third-party cookies or enable "Do Not Track" in your browser.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-brand-navy mt-6">Data storage</h3>
      <p>
        Form submissions are stored in a Notion database (servers outside Hong Kong) and email notifications are sent via Resend.
        Reasonable technical and organisational measures are applied to protect your data.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-brand-navy mt-6">Your rights</h3>
      <p>
        You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by emailing <a href="mailto:horsorion@gmail.com">horsorion@gmail.com</a>.
        We will respond within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-brand-navy mt-6">Governing law</h3>
      <p>This policy is governed by the laws of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
